      "note": "The P-CSCF is rejecting 100% of SIP requests because its interactions with the PCF for QoS authorization are failing. This has brought down all IMS services."
    }
  },
  "hypotheses": [
    {
      "id": "h1",
      "statement": "The MongoDB container has exited, causing the PCF to fail its policy-authorization procedures. This leads to the P-CSCF rejecting all SIP INVITE and REGISTER requests with a 412 error, causing a complete outage of VoNR services.",
      "primary_suspect_nf": "pcf",
